snippet.title: I Quit.
snippet.description:
Hey, everyone. It's me, Quackity. I just want to share with everyone that I am approaching a new phase in my life. This video has been in the works for a long time, and I hope everyone can watch in it's entirety. Nearly three years ago I inadvertently quit my main platform where I was making content, and ever since then, I‚Äôve been working on a lot of projects which I am incredibly proud of.

Today, I want to announce my biggest project yet.

Dababel.

This is a project which I hold very dear to my heart, not because of what it is, but because of what it represents to me. I was born and raised in Mexico, my native language is Spanish - and this gave me the opportunity to experience what it was like to be in another country and not know the language. Throughout my life and my career I‚Äôve noticed how prevalent language barriers are - no matter where you are. And Dababel is a project with the objective to help people move beyond this barrier, which has existed since the beginning of time.

This is a project for you. This is a project for everyone.

DABABEL IS FOR THE WORLD. 

Thank you for all the support, and I hope you enjoy Dababel. To my global communities, to my new viewers and old, thank you for everything!

snippet.title: Timelapse shows Texas flash floods turn dry river into deadly rapids in 20 minutes
snippet.description:
Dramatic timelapse video shows how heavy rainfall turned a dry riverbed into surging rapids in just 20 minutes, as Texas was deluged by deadly flash floods on July 4.

CCTV footage shows water begin surging into the Llano River at 17:14. Within minutes, a road crossing the river is entirely submerged, with the waterline rising significantly on both sides of the riverbank and completely covering trees and bushes.

snippet.title: Jay Leno's ULTIMATE GM Restomods: Buick, Chevy, & Oldsmobile! | Jay Leno's Garage
snippet.description:
Join Jay Leno in a special episode of Jay Leno's Garage as he showcases three incredible General Motors restomods that were built for SEMA, including a Hot Rod of the Year winner! With the invaluable help of GM engineers like Tony Roma, these classic American cars have been transformed into modern powerhouses while retaining their iconic styling.

1. The 1955 Buick Roadmaster: Jay recounts the personal history of his '55 Buick, from buying it out of the PennySaver to getting married in it. See how it was transformed with a 572 crate engine, C5 Corvette suspension, and disc brakes, making this vintage Buick able to "blow off a Corvette!" 

2. The 1932 Bowtie Deuce Roadster:

 Celebrating the 50th anniversary of the small-block V8, this '32 Chevy body sits on a '34 Chevy chassis and is powered by a 427 LS7 engine with 600 horsepower and a 6-speed manual gearbox. Discover the unique diamond-infused paint  and the challenges of building a classic hot rod with modern performance.

3. The 1966 Oldsmobile Toronado:

The Hot Rod of the Year winner in 2006, this Toronado is a true marvel. Originally a groundbreaking front-wheel-drive car , Jay's restomod features a custom chassis, a 427 LS7 engine with twin turbochargers , and over 1000 horsepower! Learn about its unique engineering, including custom-made wheels and a solid 50/50 weight distribution.

Experience these "bulletproof" builds, the challenges of working with extreme power, and the joy of driving these American legends!

localized.title: Jay Leno's ULTIMATE GM Restomods: Buick, Chevy, & Oldsmobile! | Jay Leno's Garage
localized.description:
Join Jay Leno in a special episode of Jay Leno's Garage as he showcases three incredible General Motors restomods that were built for SEMA, including a Hot Rod of the Year winner! With the invaluable help of GM engineers like Tony Roma, these classic American cars have been transformed into modern powerhouses while retaining their iconic styling.

1. The 1955 Buick Roadmaster: Jay recounts the personal history of his '55 Buick, from buying it out of the PennySaver to getting married in it. See how it was transformed with a 572 crate engine, C5 Corvette suspension, and disc brakes, making this vintage Buick able to "blow off a Corvette!" 

2. The 1932 Bowtie Deuce Roadster:

 Celebrating the 50th anniversary of the small-block V8, this '32 Chevy body sits on a '34 Chevy chassis and is powered by a 427 LS7 engine with 600 horsepower and a 6-speed manual gearbox. Discover the unique diamond-infused paint  and the challenges of building a classic hot rod with modern performance.

3. The 1966 Oldsmobile Toronado:

The Hot Rod of the Year winner in 2006, this Toronado is a true marvel. Originally a groundbreaking front-wheel-drive car , Jay's restomod features a custom chassis, a 427 LS7 engine with twin turbochargers , and over 1000 horsepower! Learn about its unique engineering, including custom-made wheels and a solid 50/50 weight distribution.

Experience these "bulletproof" builds, the challenges of working with extreme power, and the joy of driving these American legends!

nl-NL.title: Jay Leno's ULTIEME GM Restomods: Buick, Chevy en Oldsmobile! | Jay Leno's Garage
nl-NL.description:
Sluit je aan bij Jay Leno in een speciale aflevering van Jay Leno's Garage, waarin hij drie ongelooflijke General Motors restomods laat zien die speciaal voor SEMA zijn gebouwd, waaronder een Hot Rod of the Year-winnaar! Met de onschatbare hulp van GM-ingenieurs zoals Tony Roma zijn deze klassieke Amerikaanse auto's omgetoverd tot moderne krachtpatsers, met behoud van hun iconische stijl.

1. De Buick Roadmaster uit 1955: Jay vertelt over de persoonlijke geschiedenis van zijn Buick uit '55, van de aankoop uit de PennySaver tot zijn huwelijk erin. Zie hoe hij werd omgebouwd met een 572 kratmotor, C5 Corvette-vering en schijfremmen, waardoor deze vintage Buick "een Corvette kan overtreffen!" 2. De Bowtie Deuce Roadster uit 1932:

Deze '32 Chevy-carrosserie, die het 50-jarig jubileum van de small-block V8 viert, staat op een '34 Chevy-chassis en wordt aangedreven door een 427 LS7-motor met 600 pk en een handgeschakelde zesversnellingsbak. Ontdek de unieke diamantge√Ønfuseerde lak en de uitdagingen van het bouwen van een klassieke hot rod met moderne prestaties.

3. De Oldsmobile Toronado uit 1966:

Deze Toronado, winnaar van de Hot Rod of the Year-prijs in 2006, is een waar wonder. Oorspronkelijk een baanbrekende auto met voorwielaandrijving, beschikt Jay's restomod over een aangepast chassis, een 427 LS7-motor met dubbele turbo en meer dan 1000 pk! Ontdek de unieke techniek, inclusief op maat gemaakte velgen en een solide 50/50-gewichtsverdeling.

Ervaar deze "kogelvrije" bouwwerken, de uitdagingen van het werken met extreme kracht en het plezier van het besturen van deze Amerikaanse legendes!

id.title: GM Restomod TERBAIK Jay Leno: Buick, Chevy, & Oldsmobile! | Garasi Jay Leno
id.description:
Bergabunglah dengan Jay Leno dalam episode spesial Jay Leno's Garage saat ia memamerkan tiga mobil General Motors yang luar biasa yang dibuat untuk SEMA, termasuk pemenang Hot Rod of the Year! Dengan bantuan tak ternilai dari para insinyur GM seperti Tony Roma, mobil-mobil klasik Amerika ini telah diubah menjadi mobil-mobil modern yang bertenaga sambil mempertahankan gaya ikoniknya.

1. Buick Roadmaster 1955: Jay menceritakan sejarah pribadi Buick '55 miliknya, dari membelinya dari PennySaver hingga menikah di dalamnya. Lihat bagaimana mobil itu diubah dengan mesin 572 crate, suspensi C5 Corvette, dan rem cakram, yang membuat Buick klasik ini mampu "melampaui Corvette!" 

2. Bowtie Deuce Roadster 1932:

Merayakan ulang tahun ke-50 mesin V8 blok kecil, bodi Chevy '32 ini berada di atas sasis Chevy '34 dan ditenagai oleh mesin 427 LS7 dengan tenaga 600 tenaga kuda dan transmisi manual 6 percepatan. Temukan cat unik yang diresapi berlian dan tantangan dalam membangun mobil hot rod klasik dengan performa modern.

3. Oldsmobile Toronado 1966:

Pemenang Hot Rod of the Year pada tahun 2006, Toronado ini benar-benar luar biasa. Awalnya merupakan mobil penggerak roda depan yang inovatif, restomod Jay menampilkan sasis khusus, mesin 427 LS7 dengan turbocharger ganda, dan lebih dari 1000 tenaga kuda! Pelajari tentang rekayasa uniknya, termasuk roda yang dibuat khusus dan distribusi berat 50/50 yang solid.

Rasakan pengalaman membangun kendaraan "antipeluru" ini, tantangan bekerja dengan tenaga ekstrem, dan kegembiraan mengendarai legenda Amerika ini!

en.title: Jay Leno's ULTIMATE GM Restomods: Buick, Chevy, & Oldsmobile! | Jay Leno's Garage
en.description:
Join Jay Leno in a special episode of Jay Leno's Garage as he showcases three incredible General Motors restomods that were built for SEMA, including a Hot Rod of the Year winner! With the invaluable help of GM engineers like Tony Roma, these classic American cars have been transformed into modern powerhouses while retaining their iconic styling.

1. The 1955 Buick Roadmaster: Jay recounts the personal history of his '55 Buick, from buying it out of the PennySaver to getting married in it. See how it was transformed with a 572 crate engine, C5 Corvette suspension, and disc brakes, making this vintage Buick able to "blow off a Corvette!" 

2. The 1932 Bowtie Deuce Roadster:

 Celebrating the 50th anniversary of the small-block V8, this '32 Chevy body sits on a '34 Chevy chassis and is powered by a 427 LS7 engine with 600 horsepower and a 6-speed manual gearbox. Discover the unique diamond-infused paint  and the challenges of building a classic hot rod with modern performance.

3. The 1966 Oldsmobile Toronado:

The Hot Rod of the Year winner in 2006, this Toronado is a true marvel. Originally a groundbreaking front-wheel-drive car , Jay's restomod features a custom chassis, a 427 LS7 engine with twin turbochargers , and over 1000 horsepower! Learn about its unique engineering, including custom-made wheels and a solid 50/50 weight distribution.

Experience these "bulletproof" builds, the challenges of working with extreme power, and the joy of driving these American legends!

it.title: Le migliori Restomod GM di Jay Leno: Buick, Chevy e Oldsmobile! | Garage di Jay Leno
it.description:
Unisciti a Jay Leno in una puntata speciale di Jay Leno's Garage, che presenta tre incredibili restomod della General Motors costruite per il SEMA, tra cui una vincitrice del premio Hot Rod of the Year! Con il prezioso aiuto di ingegneri GM come Tony Roma, queste classiche auto americane sono state trasformate in moderni propulsori, pur mantenendo il loro stile iconico.

1. La Buick Roadmaster del 1955: Jay racconta la storia personale della sua Buick del '55, dall'acquisto da PennySaver al matrimonio a bordo. Scopri come √® stata trasformata con un motore 572 a cassa, sospensioni da Corvette C5 e freni a disco, rendendo questa Buick d'epoca in grado di "spazzare via una Corvette!".

2. Bowtie Deuce Roadster del 1932:

Per celebrare il 50¬∞ anniversario del motore V8 small-block, questa Chevy del '32 √® costruita su un telaio Chevy del '34 ed √® alimentata da un motore 427 LS7 da 600 cavalli e cambio manuale a 6 marce. Scopri l'esclusiva vernice diamantata e le sfide che comporta costruire una hot rod classica con prestazioni moderne.

3. Oldsmobile Toronado del 1966:

Vincitrice del premio Hot Rod dell'Anno nel 2006, questa Toronado √® una vera meraviglia. Originariamente un'auto rivoluzionaria a trazione anteriore, la restomod di Jay presenta un telaio personalizzato, un motore 427 LS7 con doppio turbocompressore e oltre 1000 cavalli di potenza! Scopri la sua ingegneria unica, inclusi i cerchi su misura e una solida distribuzione del peso 50/50.

Scopri queste build "a prova di proiettile", le sfide di lavorare con una potenza estrema e la gioia di guidare queste leggende americane!

snippet.title: THIS PIZZA CHALLENGE IN FLORIDA HAS ONLY BEEN BEATEN ONCE! | BeardMeatsFood
snippet.description:
In this week's episode we're at Crostini's Pizza & Cuisine in Deltona, Florida having a crack at their 28" pizza challenge...

Teams of two get just 28 minutes in which to finish a 28" pizza (with toppings of their choice...or just plain cheese if you're feeling a bit soggy) and if successful, not only is the meal ON THE HOUSE but you get a $50 gift card for your troubles too! It's been a while since I tried a team pizza challenge, so I gave my old mate @WayneAlgenio a call to help me try to secure the win!

snippet.title: Floods devastate Texas hill country as death toll approaches 70
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump has approved federal disaster assistance for the state of Texas to assist in recovery efforts after massive floods destroyed dozens of homes and killed nearly 70 people. The funding is available to affected individuals in Kerr County, with assistance including grants for temporary housing and home repairs, low-cost loans to cover uninsured property, and various other recovery programs. Funding will also be available to state and local governments, as well as certain nonprofits, for emergency work and the repair of critical infrastructure, as well as the repair or replacement of facilities.

snippet.title: How do Minecraft computers work?
snippet.description:
Today I learn to build Minecraft redstone computers, with expert lesson from Computational Redstone YouTuber  @mattbatwings   . Mattbatwings has built pacman in Minecraft, Super Mario Bros in Minecraft, Flappy bird in Minecraft and so much more - a lot of these giant redstone contraptions are featured in this video. Matt also does a tutorial on Computational redstone, covering the fundaments of Minecraft redstone logic, and even gets me to build my first computational redstone contraption.

MATTS CHANNEL: https://www.youtube.com/@mattbatwings
GO WATCH EVERYTHING HE HAS MADE!!

id.title: Saya Mencoba Pelayaran Mewah Ritz Carlton
id.description:
Mulailah dengan Odoo hari ini: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR 
Saya akan naik ke salah satu kapal pesiar termewah di dunia, Ritz Carlton Yacht yang baru, Ilma. Saya telah memesan suite khusus untuk 7 hari ke depan, dan saya akan menunjukkan kepada Anda semua yang ditawarkan kapal Kelas Utama ini. Dari banyak restoran (termasuk menu mencicipi 10 hidangan seharga $700!), kolam renang, marina terapung, dan kita bahkan akan melihat kamar terbaik di atas kapal, suite pemilik.

Sebenarnya ini bukan pertama kalinya saya naik Ritz Carlton Yacht, setelah mencoba kapal mereka sebelumnya Evrima beberapa tahun yang lalu. Ada beberapa masalah awal di atas pelayaran itu, jadi saya ingin melihat bagaimana mereka telah berubah (atau apakah mereka telah berubah!) dengan penambahan Ilma dan Luminara. nl-NL.title: Ik heb een ultra-luxe Ritz Carlton-cruise geprobeerd
nl-NL.description:
Begin vandaag nog met Odoo: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR
Ik ga aan boord van een van 's werelds meest luxueuze cruiseschepen, de gloednieuwe Ritz Carlton Yacht, de Ilma. Ik heb een signature suite geboekt voor de komende 7 dagen en ik laat je alles zien wat dit eersteklas schip te bieden heeft. Van de vele restaurants (inclusief een 10-gangen proeverijmenu voor $ 700!), de zwembaden, de drijvende jachthaven, tot de beste kamer aan boord: de eigenaarssuite.

Ter referentie: zoals gewoonlijk heb ik deze cruise volledig betaald, omdat ik niet met rederijen werk, voor meer dan $ 28.000! Het is niet de eerste keer dat ik aan boord ga van een Ritz Carlton Yacht. Ik heb een paar jaar geleden hun vorige schip, de Evrima, geprobeerd. Er waren nogal wat kinderziektes aan boord van die cruise, dus ik ben benieuwd hoe ze zijn veranderd (of dat ze dat al zijn!) met de toevoeging van Ilma en Luminara. Deze nieuwe schepen zijn groter, met nog meer hutten en faciliteiten. Laat me zoals altijd hieronder weten wat je ervan vindt.

it.title: Ho provato una crociera ultra lusso Ritz Carlton
it.description:
Inizia subito con Odoo: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR
Salgo a bordo di una delle navi da crociera pi√π lussuose al mondo, il nuovissimo Ritz Carlton Yacht, Ilma. Ho prenotato una suite esclusiva per i prossimi 7 giorni e vi mostrer√≤ tutto ci√≤ che questa nave di Prima Classe ha da offrire. Dai numerosi ristoranti (incluso un menu degustazione di 10 portate a 700 dollari!), alle piscine, al porto turistico galleggiante, e daremo persino un'occhiata alla migliore camera a bordo, la suite armatoriale.

Come al solito, ho pagato per intero questa crociera, dato che non lavoro con le compagnie di crociera, per un totale di oltre 28.000 dollari! In realt√† non √® la mia prima volta a bordo di un Ritz Carlton Yacht, avendo provato la loro precedente nave, l'Evrima, un paio di anni fa. Ci sono stati parecchi problemi iniziali a bordo di quella nave, quindi sono curioso di vedere come sono cambiati (o se lo sono cambiati!) con l'aggiunta di Ilma e Luminara. Queste nuove navi sono pi√π grandi, con ancora pi√π cabine e servizi. Come sempre, fatemi sapere cosa ne pensate qui sotto.

snippet.title: Search and recovery efforts continue across the flood ravaged Hill Country
snippet.description:
Flash floods in Texas killed at least 82 people over the Fourth of July holiday weekend and left others still missing, including girls attending a summer camp. The devastation along the Guadalupe River, outside of San Antonio, has drawn a massive search effort as officials face questions over their preparedness and the speed of their initial actions.

snippet.title: Death toll in central Texas flash floods rises to 79 as sheriff says 10 campers remain missing
snippet.description:
Families sifted through waterlogged debris Sunday and stepped inside empty cabins at Camp Mystic, an all-girls summer camp ripped apart by flash floods that washed homes off their foundations and killed at least 79 people in central Texas.

Rescuers maneuvering through challenging terrain continued their desperate search for the missing, including 10 girls and a counselor from the camp. For the first time since the storms began pounding Texas, Gov. Greg Abbott said there were 41 people confirmed to be unaccounted for across the state and more could be missing.

Read more at: https://www.9news.com/article/news/nation-world/texas-floods-campers-missing/507-2c41ffb5-638c-4d53-bc6b-a444a0618bdb

snippet.title: The evidence that damned Piastri in Verstappen British GP controversy
snippet.description:
A penalty for erratic driving decided the British Grand Prix as an aggrieved Oscar Piastri lost victory to McLaren team-mate and F1 title rival Lando Norris. 

This wet and wild Silverstone F1 race came down to one key moment: the restart on lap 21, when Piastri‚Äôs braking caught Verstappen out. Jon Noble and Scott Mitchell-Malm delve into the data that doomed Piastri.

00:00 How Piastri lost victory
01:43 Piastri's double trouble
03:10 Verstappen's view
04:17 Why Canada was different
05:40 McLaren suggests gamesmanship
07:48 Piastri's cheeky swap request
08:46 Title race implications

snippet.title: Texas flooding survivor & witness reaction to Kerrville damage, search & rescues: 'Complete shock'
snippet.description:
A Kerrville resident said he and his wife were taken 200 feet down the Guadalupe River and managed to survive while his home was damaged by the flooding.

"It was scary," Scott Walden said while describing the speed of which the water rose. "It was really scary."

Meanwhile, a Pennsylvania woman visiting family in the area said she remains in shock, especially given the volume of missing adults and children, many from Camp Mystic.

"It's not going to be a good ending," Tonia Fucci said. "There's no way people could have survived the swiftness of the water."

snippet.title: Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
David is dead. But Night City lives on.
Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 is now in production!

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 presents a new standalone 10-episode story from the world of Cyberpunk 2077‚Äî a raw chronicle of redemption and revenge. In a city that thrives in the spotlight of violence, one question remains: when the world is blinded by spectacle, what extremes do you have to go to make your story matter?

Director Kai Ikarashi (Cyberpunk: Edgerunners, SSSS.Gridman) brings a bold, cinematic vision to the series, supported by the lead character designer Kanno Ichigo (Promare, Cyberpunk: Edgerunners). They're joined by returning collaborators Masahiko Otsuka (Gurren Lagann, Promare) and Hugo Award winner Bartosz Sztybor as Showrunner, Story Writer, and Producer.

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 is created in collaboration with CD PROJEKT RED and animation studio TRIGGER, with a planned release on Netflix in the future.

snippet.title: Belton, Texas teen rescued from deadly Guadalupe River floods
snippet.description:
BELTON, Texas (KWTX) - Belton teenager Riata Schoepf was rescue by first responders on Friday after being swept away by the deadly Guadalupe River floods.

Riata went on vacation to Hunt, Texas with another family for the Fourth of July. Their hotel bordered the Guadalupe River. Her dad, Ronnie Schoepf, recalled his daughters experience being evacuated.

‚ÄúShe says around 2:30 or so she‚Äôs hearing loud thunder and lightning and then the next thing she knew somebody‚Äôs banging on her door telling everybody they need to get out,‚Äù Ronnie said.

Riata and her group took to their vehicles to escape the flooding, but traffic was at a standstill. Water then began to rise around their car.

snippet.title: Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 | Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
David is dead. But Night City lives on.

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 is now in production!

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 presents a new standalone 10-episode story from the world of Cyberpunk 2077‚Äî a raw chronicle of redemption and revenge. In a city that thrives in the spotlight of violence, one question remains: when the world is blinded by spectacle, what extremes do you have to go to make your story matter?

Director Kai Ikarashi (Cyberpunk: Edgerunners, SSSS.Gridman) brings a bold, cinematic vision to the series, supported by the lead character designer Kanno Ichigo (Promare, Cyberpunk: Edgerunners). They're joined by returning collaborators Masahiko Otsuka (Gurren Lagann, Promare) and Hugo Award winner Bartosz Sztybor as Showrunner, Story Writer, and Producer.

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 is created in collaboration with CD PROJEKT RED and animation studio TRIGGER, with a planned release on Netflix in the future.

Music: ‚ÄúDive‚Äù by Beach House. Licensed courtesy of Sub Pop Records.

snippet.title: Texas Flood Tragedy: Husband Swept Away While Camping, Wife Still Missing | Kerr County Devastation
snippet.description:
A heartbreaking story out of Kerr County, Texas, where catastrophic flooding has displaced families and left many searching for loved ones. Brian Eids recounts the terrifying moment floodwaters swept him and his wife away from their campsite ‚Äî he survived, but she remains missing. 

This report from KXAN‚Äôs Brianna Hollis captures the emotional toll as survivors gather at a reunification center in Ingram, desperately seeking updates. Governor Greg Abbott is expected to speak later tonight.

snippet.title: SPIRIT EMPRESS: Two Forms, One Card!
snippet.description:
X ‚ñ∫ https://twitter.com/ClashRoyale/
Instagram ‚ñ∫ https://www.instagram.com/clashroyale
TikTok ‚ñ∫ https://www.tiktok.com/@clashroyale
Facebook ‚ñ∫ https://www.facebook.com/ClashRoyale/

ENTER THE ARENA
Build your Battle Deck and outsmart the enemy in fast real-time battles. From the creators of CLASH OF CLANS comes a real-time multiplayer battle game starring your favourite Clash characters and more. Start battling against players from around the world!

BECOME A MASTER OF STRATEGY AND DECK BUILDING
Choose unique Cards to your Battle Deck and head to the Arena for Battle!
Place your Cards right and knock down the enemy King and Princesses from their Towers in a strategic and fast-paced match.

COLLECT AND UPGRADE 100+ CARDS
Hog Rider! Collect and upgrade 100+ Cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defences you know and love and many others. Win battles and progress to new Arenas to unlock powerful new Cards to your collection!

BATTLE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP
Battle your way to the League and Global Tournaments to match against the best players in the world.
Compete for glory and rewards!

SEASONAL EVENTS

snippet.title: Jason Momoa Causes CHAOS in the Pit at Ozzy Osbourne's Final Show
snippet.description:
We knew this show would be legendary, and Birmingham did not disappoint! This massive event was a monumental celebration of Ozzy Osborne and Black Sabbath, featuring a "who's who" of rock royalty. We witnessed incredible performances from Lizzy Hale, Papa V's epic "Bark at the Moon," Alice in Chains, and Lamb of God. The Slayer reunion, honoring Black Sabbath and Ozzy, was absolutely showstopping.

But the moment that truly broke the internet? Host Jason Momoa, during Pantera's absolutely crushing set, couldn't resist the call of the pit! He jumped in, completely lost in the moment, joining the mosh pit for Pantera's entire performance of "Hostel." Eyewitnesses saw him hugging fans and taking selfies ‚Äì a true testament to his love for the music. This historic party in Birmingham is still rocking, and Jason Momoa's sincerity and passion are undeniable!

localized.title: Jason Momoa Causes CHAOS in the Pit at Ozzy Osbourne's Final Show
localized.description:
We knew this show would be legendary, and Birmingham did not disappoint! This massive event was a monumental celebration of Ozzy Osborne and Black Sabbath, featuring a "who's who" of rock royalty. We witnessed incredible performances from Lizzy Hale, Papa V's epic "Bark at the Moon," Alice in Chains, and Lamb of God. The Slayer reunion, honoring Black Sabbath and Ozzy, was absolutely showstopping.

But the moment that truly broke the internet? Host Jason Momoa, during Pantera's absolutely crushing set, couldn't resist the call of the pit! He jumped in, completely lost in the moment, joining the mosh pit for Pantera's entire performance of "Hostel." Eyewitnesses saw him hugging fans and taking selfies ‚Äì a true testament to his love for the music. This historic party in Birmingham is still rocking, and Jason Momoa's sincerity and passion are undeniable!

en.description:
"Chainsaw Man ‚Äì The Movie: Reze Arc" - Main Trailer

"Chainsaw Man ‚Äì The Movie: Reze Arc"
In theaters 2025.09.19 (Fri)
Theme Song: Kenshi Yonezu "IRIS OUT"(Sony Music Labels Inc.)

=============== 
"Chainsaw Man ‚Äì The Movie: Reze Arc"

‚óºÔ∏éINTRODUCTION 
Extravagant bloody battle involving love and desire, humans and devils, is coming to the big screens! 

‚ÄúChainsaw Man‚Äù is a manga serialized in Shueisha‚Äôs ‚ÄúShonen Jump+‚Äù that has sold over 30,000,000 copies. In 2022, the series was broadcast as a TV Anime series that was made by animation studio MAPPA (Notable works: ‚ÄúJUJUTSU KAISEN‚Äù, ‚ÄúAttack on Titan Final Season‚Äù, etc.), creating buzz all over the world.
Now in 2025, the episode that made the world go wild during its serialization is coming to theaters as an animated movie!

‚óºÔ∏éSTORY 
Denji (Kikunosuke Toya) became ‚ÄúChainsaw Man‚Äù, a boy with a devil‚Äôs heart, and is now part of Special Division 4‚Äôs devil hunters. After a date with Makima (Tomori Kusunoki), the woman of his dreams, Denji takes shelter from the rain and meets a girl called Reze (Reina Ueda).
The girl who works at a nearby caf√© gives him a gentle smile, and they quickly grow close.
From this encounter onward, Denji's everyday life begins to change.

‚óºÔ∏éSTAFF

snippet.title: MKOI vs. BLG | CFO vs. T1 ‚Äî MSI 2025 ‚Äî Bracket Stage
snippet.description:
MSI 2025, LIVE FROM VANCOUVER #msi2025 

The 2025 League of Legends Mid-Season Invitational is here‚Äîbringing together the five regions to battle for glory, pride, and a critical edge heading into Worlds. As the second international showdown on the LoL Esports calendar, MSI pits two representatives from each regional league against one another in a high-stakes clash that tests their mettle at the season‚Äôs halfway mark. More than just a trophy is on the line: the winning team and the next best-performing region will earn extra slots at the World Championship, raising the stakes even higher. This year, the action unfolds beginning June 27 at the iconic Pacific Coliseum in Vancouver, Canada. Get ready for rivalries, redemption arcs, and unforgettable plays as pros will be challenged to Ignite The Fire Within.

PLAY-INS STAGE: June 27-June 29
BRACKET STAGE: July 1-July 12

You can always learn more and view the full match schedule at http://www.lolesports.com.

nl-NL.title: Een interstellair object zoals Oumuamua is zojuist ons zonnestelsel binnengekomen: wetenschappers...
nl-NL.description:
Astronomen hebben zojuist iets heel vreemds door ons zonnestelsel zien bewegen ‚Äì en het lijkt onze kant op te komen. Men vermoedt dat dit mysterieuze object van buiten ons zonnestelsel komt, wat het mogelijk pas de derde interstellaire bezoeker maakt die ooit is ontdekt.

Het wordt momenteel 3I/ATLAS genoemd en werd voor het eerst gezien in gegevens die tussen 25 en 29 juni werden verzameld door een systeem genaamd ATLAS ‚Äì het Asteroid Terrestrial-impact Last Alert System. Dit systeem gebruikt krachtige telescopen op Hawa√Ø en Zuid-Afrika om de nachtelijke hemel automatisch af te speuren naar ongewone of potentieel gevaarlijke ruimteobjecten.
Nadat het object was opgemerkt, werd het bevestigd door experts van NASA's Center for Near-Earth Object Studies en het Minor Planet Center van de Internationale Astronomische Unie. Dat betekent dat het niet zomaar een storing of vergissing is ‚Äì dit is echt.

Wat 3I/ATLAS zo fascinerend maakt, is de vreemde snelheid en onbekende aard ervan. Wetenschappers weten nog steeds niet wat het precies is ‚Äì het zou een komeet, een astero√Øde of misschien zelfs iets wat we nog nooit eerder hebben gezien kunnen zijn. Een bekende astronoom, Avi Loeb van Harvard University ‚Äì die beroemd werd door zijn suggestie dat ‚ÄòOumuamua mogelijk een buitenaardse sonde was ‚Äì heeft zich opnieuw uitgesproken. Dit keer stelt hij voor dat wetenschappers de krachtige James Webb-ruimtetelescoop gebruiken om dit nieuw ontdekte interstellaire object gedetailleerder te bestuderen.

Para astronom baru saja menemukan sesuatu yang sangat aneh bergerak melalui tata surya kita ‚Äî dan tampaknya benda itu akan menuju ke arah kita. Objek misterius ini diyakini berasal dari luar tata surya kita, sehingga mungkin menjadi pengunjung antarbintang ketiga yang pernah ditemukan.

Saat ini, objek tersebut disebut 3I/ATLAS, dan pertama kali terlihat dalam data yang dikumpulkan antara 25 Juni dan 29 Juni oleh sistem yang disebut ATLAS ‚Äî Asteroid Terrestrial-impact Last Alert System. Sistem ini menggunakan teleskop canggih di Hawaii dan Afrika Selatan untuk memindai langit malam secara otomatis untuk mencari objek luar angkasa yang tidak biasa atau berpotensi berbahaya.

Setelah objek tersebut terlihat, hal itu dikonfirmasi oleh para ahli di Pusat Studi Objek Dekat Bumi NASA dan Pusat Planet Minor Persatuan Astronomi Internasional. Itu berarti bahwa objek ini bukan sekadar kesalahan atau kekeliruan ‚Äî benda ini nyata.

Yang membuat 3I/ATLAS begitu menarik adalah kecepatannya yang aneh dan sifatnya yang tidak diketahui. Para ilmuwan masih belum yakin apa sebenarnya objek itu ‚Äî bisa jadi itu adalah komet, asteroid, atau bahkan sesuatu yang belum pernah kita lihat sebelumnya. Seorang astronom terkenal, Avi Loeb dari Universitas Harvard ‚Äî yang terkenal karena menyatakan bahwa ‚ÄòOumuamua mungkin adalah wahana antariksa alien ‚Äî telah memberikan tanggapan lagi. Kali ini, ia menyarankan agar para ilmuwan menggunakan Teleskop Luar Angkasa James Webb yang canggih untuk mempelajari objek antarbintang yang baru ditemukan ini secara lebih rinci.

Attualmente si chiama 3I/ATLAS ed √® stato avvistato per la prima volta nei dati raccolti tra il 25 e il 29 giugno da un sistema chiamato ATLAS, l'Asteroid Terrestrial-impact Last Alert System. Questo sistema utilizza potenti telescopi alle Hawaii e in Sudafrica per scansionare automaticamente il cielo notturno alla ricerca di oggetti spaziali insoliti o potenzialmente pericolosi.

Gli scienziati non sono ancora certi di cosa si tratti effettivamente: potrebbe essere una cometa, un asteroide o forse persino qualcosa che non abbiamo mai visto prima. Un noto astronomo, Avi Loeb dell'Universit√† di Harvard, che ha notoriamente ipotizzato che 'Oumuamua potesse essere una sonda aliena, √® tornato a dare il suo contributo. ABOUT CHELSEA FOOTBALL CLUB 

Founded in 1905, Chelsea Football Club is an English professional football club based in Fulham, West London with Stamford Bridge as the home of the club. Competing in the Premier League - the top division of English football, the club has had many successes, winning five Premier League titles. The club won their first major honour, the League championship in 1955, followed by the FA Cup in 1970, their first European honour, the Cup Winners' Cup in 1971, and became the third English club to win the Club World Cup in 2022. 

As the Pride of London, Chelsea FC is one of the most successful clubs in terms of overall trophies won. They are the only club to have won all three major European competitions twice and have taken the crown domestically, winning six league titles, eight FA Cups, five League Cups, and four FA Community Shields. Internationally, Chelsea have won the UEFA Champions League, the UEFA Europa League, the UEFA Cup Winners' Cup and the UEFA Super Cup twice each, and the FIFA Club World Cup once since their inception.

The Chelsea YouTube channel provides access to all the build-up, training and behind-the-scenes moments and matchday action along with all the unseen edits and player focus from Reece James, Cole Palmer and Enzo Fernandez to Sam Kerr, Lauren James and many more. snippet.title: Wait...The Worst Possible US Disaster Just Got EVEN WORSE?!? (Cascadia Megaquake)
snippet.description:
The Big One is coming and it could be far worse than anyone imagined.

The Cascadia Subduction Zone, just off the Pacific Northwest coast, is building toward a massive earthquake and tsunami. But new research reveals an even more terrifying possibility: widespread toxic spills, infrastructure collapse, wildfires, and deadly gas plumes. All triggered by a single seismic event.

In this episode of Weathered, we dig into the science behind the Cascadia Megaquake, why the Pacific Northwest is especially vulnerable, and how climate change could make it worse. We explore what you can do to stay safe and why your community might be your best line of defense.

snippet.title: Primitive Technology: Floating Pulley Blower Smelt
snippet.description:
Floating Pulley Blower Smelt
Subscribe: http://bit.ly/subPT | Never miss a video! Enable ‚ÄòALL‚Äô Notifications!
Watch my newest content: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLGnWLXjIDnpBR4xqf3FO-xFFwE-ucq4Fj&playnext=1&index=2

Patreon: https://patreon.com/user?u=2945881

Watch More Primitive Technology:
Newest Uploads: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLGnWLXjIDnpBR4xqf3FO-xFFwE-ucq4Fj&playnext=1&index=2
Pyrotechnology: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLGnWLXjIDnpBVRqu5lz5JGaQxjPs7q3CJ&playnext=1&index=2
Shelter: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLGnWLXjIDnpBBsdKZb-vy30o88SIxItp2&playnext=1&index=2
Weapons: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLGnWLXjIDnpA-XGDrrmVgBnSXx15i2Awp&playnext=1&index=2
Popular Videos: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLGnWLXjIDnpAb29Lrdki5BPjTpMon8zla&playnext=1&index=2

About This Video:
I tested the floating pulley blower I made last time in an iron smelt. I started by re-building the blower housing from the last project which had broken after getting wet. Then I set up the blower and tested a fixed pulley wheel that was held in place with a different configuration to the pulley wheels from the last project, where the pulley was outside of 2 stakes as opposed to between to stakes, in order to allow a crank handle to be attached directly to the wheel instead of to the rotor. But it had issues with durability so I decided to test the "floating" pulley wheel method I developed last time where the pulley has 2 handles and is held in the hands only with no support frame, spokes or hub of the fixed wheel design. The great reduction in parts makes it simpler and less likely to fail. It worked satisfactorily pushing about the same air as the "one way spinning rope stick blower" method and the "2 way spinning blower method" but with more even air flow. It gave a slightly above average yield of 21 g of cast iron prills from 1200g of ore as opposed to the normal 15 g from 1200g. This is despite the wood preheat phase of the furnace only being 25 minutes as opposed to 1 hour, preheating the furnace may be important to get the furnace to temperature before adding the charcoal and in future I'll do it for longer. Using the floating wheel isn't as tiring as I thought it might be and is comparable to the rope stick method and is much easier than the 2 way spinning method where a rope has to pulled outwards with two hands repeatedly. It is currently a good competitor to the rope stick method. However, if I want to scale up the wheel size and consequently rpm of the fan, I'll need to revisit the fixed wheel design as the floating wheel won't scale up. Overall, I see this method as a stepping stone to a better blower and better smelts in future.

00:00-05:18 New blower housing
05:18-06:51 Set up blower and furnace
06:51-08:50 Banana fibre belt & splicing
08:50-10:14 Little clay pulleys
10:14-11:33 Testing a fixed pulley design
11:33- 12:29 Making and testing floating pulley design
12:29-14:09 Replace clay pulleys with fibre wrapped rotor/test
14:09- 14:37 Smelt preparations
14:37- 17:39 Smelt
17:39- 19:09 Process bloom
19:09- 19:48 Result

About Primitive Technology:
Primitive technology is a hobby where you build things in the wild completely from scratch using no modern tools or materials. These are the strict rules: If you want a fire, use a fire stick - An axe, pick up a stone and shape it - A hut, build one from trees, mud, rocks etc. The challenge is seeing how far you can go without utilizing modern technology. I do not live in the wild, but enjoy building shelter, tools, and more, only utilizing natural materials. To find specific videos, visit my playlist tab for building videos focused on pyrotechnology, shelter, weapons, food & agriculture, tools & machines, and weaving & fiber.

But it had issues with durability so I decided to test the "floating" pulley wheel method I developed last time where the pulley has 2 handles and is held in the hands only with no support frame, spokes or hub of the fixed wheel design. The great reduction in parts makes it simpler and less likely to fail. It worked satisfactorily pushing about the same air as the "one way spinning rope stick blower" method and the "2 way spinning blower method" but with more even air flow. It gave a slightly above average yield of 21 g of cast iron prills from 1200g of ore as opposed to the normal 15 g from 1200g. This is despite the wood preheat phase of the furnace only being 25 minutes as opposed to 1 hour, preheating the furnace may be important to get the furnace to temperature before adding the charcoal and in future I'll do it for longer. Using the floating wheel isn't as tiring as I thought it might be and is comparable to the rope stick method and is much easier than the 2 way spinning method where a rope has to pulled outwards with two hands repeatedly. It is currently a good competitor to the rope stick method. However, if I want to scale up the wheel size and consequently rpm of the fan, I'll need to revisit the fixed wheel design as the floating wheel won't scale up. Overall, I see this method as a stepping stone to a better blower and better smelts in future.

05:18-06:51 Set up blower and furnace
06:51-08:50 Banana fibre belt & splicing
08:50-10:14 Little clay pulleys
10:14-11:33 Testing a fixed pulley design
11:33- 12:29 Making and testing floating pulley design
12:29-14:09 Replace clay pulleys with fibre wrapped rotor/test
14:09- 14:37 Smelt preparations
14:37- 17:39 Smelt
17:39- 19:09 Process bloom
19:09- 19:48 Result

About Primitive Technology:
Primitive technology is a hobby where you build things in the wild completely from scratch using no modern tools or materials. These are the strict rules: If you want a fire, use a fire stick - An axe, pick up a stone and shape it - A hut, build one from trees, mud, rocks etc. The challenge is seeing how far you can go without utilizing modern technology. I do not live in the wild, but enjoy building shelter, tools, and more, only utilizing natural materials. To find specific videos, visit my playlist tab for building videos focused on pyrotechnology, shelter, weapons, food & agriculture, tools & machines, and weaving & fiber.

Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation.
